  1в†’/**
  2в†’ * PRD Template Generator
  3в†’ *
  4в†’ * Shared PRD template used by AutoWorkCreation hook and algorithm.ts CLI.
  5в†’ * Generates PRD files matching the frontmatter schema expected by algorithm.ts readPRD().
  6в†’ *
  7в†’ * Used by: AutoWorkCreation.hook.ts, algorithm.ts
